_sText:
Its a medium map with the possibility to chose your own way to. If you chose the short way, then yes it gets a bit harder..

Okay there is a catch in this map and thats that you get a pretty sad choke. I know, its my own fault by making such a big map inside one skybox. But well, no one's forcing you to play it. 

I've tested the map on a 14 slot server and i got a choke on 10-40 through the map and it is possible to complete.
